channel.title: 459 server development
channel.description:
Hey.. I'm looking for someone who can make a forum, webclient. Now to the coding, as what I know at the moment, I have one guy to help me out at this part but yet waiting for his reply. As I might need two you can tell me if you wanna help or not. It's up to you if you wanna make a forum, webclient or help me/us coding.
This is a base of Project annihilation 459. Everything is the same on this as on that except for a few changes. Look up Pja and you'll know what I'm talking about. :)
These fields are required to join.
Name: Experience: Ever had a good server made: Age: How long you code: What you gonna code: How you gonna contact me: Why you wanna work on this: Do you understand Eclipse:
We're trying to make it old Runescape. Therefore it gotta be hosted 24/7. I can't host it 24/7. :|
